Takes a `boolean`. Default `true`.

If `true`, regards the sheva under the letters Ô¨™Ô¨´◊°◊¶◊†◊û◊ú◊ï◊ô when preceded by a waw-consecutive with a missing _dagesh chazaq_ as vocal. If a meteg is present, the sheva is always a _sheva na'_.

```typescript
